  <div class="strategy-page">
    <div class="strategy-container">
      <StrategyHeader date="February 1, 2026" client={clientData} strategyType="Website Redesign Strategy" />

      <div class="executive-summary">
        <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
        <p>
          This comprehensive analysis examines Specified Roofing's current website against top Toronto commercial
          roofing competitors to identify gaps and opportunities. Key findings reveal significant opportunities in user
          experience, portfolio presentation, and conversion optimization. The recommended strategy focuses on creating
          an intuitive, client-centric website that positions Specified Roofing as the preferred choice for commercial
          roofing across Canada.
        </p>
