      <h2 class="section-header">Current Website Analysis</h2>

      <div class="two-column">
        <div class="column">
          <h3>Strengths</h3>
          <ul class="content-list strength">
            <li><strong>25+ years of experience</strong> - Strong industry credibility</li>
            <li><strong>Comprehensive service offerings</strong> - Wide range of roofing systems</li>
            <li><strong>24/7 Emergency service</strong> - Critical differentiator</li>
            <li><strong>Professional associations</strong> - Multiple industry certifications</li>
            <li><strong>Geographic coverage</strong> - Canada-wide service</li>
            <li><strong>Specialized services</strong> - Infrared scanning, asset management</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="column">
          <h3>Weaknesses</h3>
          <ul class="content-list weakness">
            <li><strong>Navigation complexity</strong> - Too many nested dropdown menus</li>
            <li><strong>Limited portfolio visibility</strong> - Projects buried in subcategories</li>
            <li><strong>No clear CTAs</strong> - Homepage lacks prominent conversion paths</li>
            <li><strong>Generic terminology</strong> - Confusing technical pages</li>
            <li><strong>Minimal visual hierarchy</strong> - Text-heavy, limited imagery</li>
            <li><strong>No integrated quote tool</strong> - Multi-step contact process</li>
            <li><strong>Missing trust signals</strong> - No prominent testimonials on homepage</li>
            <li><strong>Outdated design</strong> - Does not reflect modern B2B expectations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
