          <ul class="content-list">
            <li>Clean, modern design with strong visual hierarchy</li>
            <li>Exceptional project showcase with before/after images</li>
            <li>Prominent client logos (Toyota, CN, CIBC, Starbucks)</li>
            <li>Active blog content (10+ recent articles)</li>
            <li>Since 1956 (70+ years experience)</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Key Differentiator:</h4>
          <p>Superior visual presentation and thought leadership through extensive blog content.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="competitor-card">
          <h3>Coverall Roofing</h3>
          <div class="website">coverallroofing.ca</div>
          <h4>Key Strengths:</h4>
          <ul class="content-list">
            <li>Immediate quote form on homepage</li>
            <li>7 years HomeStars Best of the Best</li>
            <li>40+ years experience prominently displayed</li>
            <li>Multiple customer testimonials on homepage</li>
            <li>Brand partner logos visible</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Key Differentiator:</h4>
          <p>Immediate conversion focus with prominent quote form and extensive social proof.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="competitor-card">
          <h3>Integrity Roofers</h3>
          <div class="website">integrityroofers.com</div>
          <h4>Key Strengths:</h4>
          <ul class="content-list">
            <li>20+ years experience</li>
            <li>Clear commercial B2B positioning</li>
            <li>Warranty focus messaging</li>
            <li>FAQ section for common questions</li>
            <li>Transparency emphasis</li>
          </ul>
          <h4>Key Differentiator:</h4>
          <p>Process transparency and warranty-backed quality commitment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Gap Analysis -->
      <h2 class="section-header">Gap Analysis & Opportunities</h2>

      <div class="content-block">
        <div class="highlight-box danger">
          <h4>Critical Gaps Identified</h4>
          <p>
            Analysis reveals 7 major areas where competitors outperform current website, creating significant
            opportunities for competitive advantage through strategic improvements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <ol class="recommendation-list">
        <li>
          <h4>User Experience & Navigation</h4>
          <p>
            <strong>Gap:</strong> Complex nested menus confuse users; services and portfolio are hard to find<br />
            <strong>Competitor Advantage:</strong> Elite Roofing has clear service grouping; Coverall has simple navigation<br
            />
            <strong>Opportunity:</strong> Implement flat, intuitive navigation with max 2 levels
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h4>Portfolio Presentation</h4>
          <p>
            <strong>Gap:</strong> Projects are categorized but lack visual appeal and detail<br />
            <strong>Competitor Advantage:</strong> Elite Roofing showcases projects with professional photography, case studies<br
            />
            <strong>Opportunity:</strong> Create featured project showcase on homepage with detailed case studies
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h4>Conversion Optimization</h4>
          <p>
            <strong>Gap:</strong> No immediate quote/estimate form; multiple steps to contact<br />
            <strong>Competitor Advantage:</strong> Coverall has homepage quote form; all competitors have prominent phone
            CTAs<br />
            <strong>Opportunity:</strong> Add multi-channel conversion paths (quote form, click-to-call, live chat)
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h4>Trust Signals & Social Proof</h4>
          <p>
            <strong>Gap:</strong> Awards/certifications in footer only; no customer testimonials visible<br />
            <strong>Competitor Advantage:</strong> Coverall displays 7+ years of awards; Elite shows major client logos<br
            />
            <strong>Opportunity:</strong> Prominently display awards, certifications, testimonials, client logos
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h4>Content Marketing</h4>
          <p>
            <strong>Gap:</strong> No blog or resource center<br />
            <strong>Competitor Advantage:</strong> Elite has active blog with 10+ recent articles<br />
            <strong>Opportunity:</strong> Launch blog with educational content (ROI calculator, maintenance guides)
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h4>Emergency Service Visibility</h4>
          <p>
            <strong>Gap:</strong> Emergency service exists but not immediately visible<br />
            <strong>Competitor Advantage:</strong> Multiple competitors feature emergency numbers in header<br />
            <strong>Opportunity:</strong> Sticky emergency banner with 60-minute response promise
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h4>Client Portal & Tools</h4>
          <p>
            <strong>Gap:</strong> No online tools for clients<br />
            <strong>Competitor Advantage:</strong> Elite has online invoice payment<br />
            <strong>Opportunity:</strong> Client login for project tracking, document access, payments
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>

