        <li><strong>Clarity over complexity</strong> - Simple navigation, clear messaging</li>
        <li><strong>Visual storytelling</strong> - Show, don't just tell through imagery</li>
        <li><strong>Trust building</strong> - Prominent social proof and credibility indicators</li>
        <li><strong>Action-oriented</strong> - Clear next steps on every page</li>
        <li><strong>Educational value</strong> - Help clients make informed decisions</li>
      </ul>

