      <h2 class="section-header">Conclusion</h2>

      <div class="executive-summary">
        <p>
          The current Specified Roofing website has strong foundational content but lacks the modern UX, visual appeal,
          and conversion optimization necessary to compete in today's digital landscape. By implementing the recommended
          sitemap, page strategies, and design improvements, Specified Roofing will make it easier for clients to find
          information and request quotes, showcase 25+ years of expertise through compelling project stories, build
          trust through prominent social proof, educate clients through valuable resources, convert more visitors into
          leads through optimized conversion paths, and position itself as the clear choice for commercial roofing in
